http://www.panorama.sk/en/slovak-language
  - this is basically the same, but the eshop has an English UI as well, so, if you are going to buy those textbooks, workbooks, CDs, etc. try panorama.sk instead preskoly.sk (this is a more generic eshop, it seems)
https://www.juniorpapier.sk/1561-sk/subor-slovensky-jazyk-subor-1-11.php - buy something like this to have all the cases on one sheet with you
